{"tid":2507160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國留學生實拍印度疫情：醫院過於恐怖被禁拍照　藥師稱不怕得病","createTime":"2021-04-27T23:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T01:01:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9beaa3e43d9c5ef35c6c8f6101f900a5f71b5210","tid":2507160,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T23:30:39.000Z","msg":"印度新冠肺炎疫情嚴重，中國留學生小陳日前上載短片，分享她在印度的見聞，稱街道上坐有不少病人；她又前往印度甘地醫院拍攝疫情情況，結果「醫院過於恐怖，被禁止拍照」。而她到藥店詢問藥劑師是否害怕感染，藥劑師則回答「不怕」，令她十分驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n影片在內地網絡引起熱議，有人提醒她疫情下要注意安全，不要到處亂跑；但更多人則是將焦點放在「女生居然敢到印度留學」，認為印度治安混亂，尤其對女性來說相當危險。<br />\n<br />\n小陳在影片中介紹，醫院禁止她拍攝，但醫院外救護車已經排滿，馬路上坐滿了病人，景象過於恐怖。此外，小陳還前往藥店詢問藥師對疫情的看法，對方淡定地表示不怕得病，還稱「得了也可以治療，吃藥就行」。<br />\n<br />\n小陳認為，印度人不在意新冠疫情，「他們的意思就是得了就得了」，又指印度當下實際感染人數遠多於目前的報告人數。<br />\n<br />\n對於小陳的影片，內地網民議論紛紛，但大多數人將焦點放在，小陳作為一個女生，為何會到印度留學，認為印度治安不佳，尤其對女生來說很危險：<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210427/463722193574957056923501.jpeg/Kvh5k6qI8eB5G74o1PRFqI_kSglMXVbamBTUIJgU1CA?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210427%2F463722193574957056923501.jpeg%2FKvh5k6qI8eB5G74o1PRFqI_kSglMXVbamBTUIJgU1CA%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=0d6ba488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國路透社4月26日消息，截至當日，印度新冠感染病例新增35萬2991宗，總感染人數已超過1700萬；死亡人數新增2812宗，累計達到19萬5123宗。但外界多認為印度的病例和死亡人數不只這些。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210427/463715359560568832765319.jpeg/Z6gkuR9yN198fPZgmKtEjrwb4O6JAOUSR-fn2Efn59g?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210427%2F463715359560568832765319.jpeg%2FZ6gkuR9yN198fPZgmKtEjrwb4O6JAOUSR-fn2Efn59g%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=4aa50e0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec54fc3ece0e29bfb30083b6ece422701fb1e3f8","tid":2507160,"uid":66324,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T23:32:15.000Z","msg":"點解會去印度留學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae134a3565d04f3a7a1ad665c7d17e16fe095aed","tid":2507160,"uid":51753,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T23:33:17.000Z","msg":"女生居然敢到印度留學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZcpjJT3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZcpjJT3.jpg&h=28ee8f8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32df31c5f8e5712c8df7de583a50c166ed9473e1","tid":2507160,"uid":375068,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ec54fc3ece0e29bfb30083b6ece422701fb1e3f8","tid":2507160,"uid":66324,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T23:32:15.000Z","msg":"點解會去印度留學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T23:33:44.000Z","msg":"佢就係播毒嗰個"},{"pid":"22a441022de1a78b9d9af37b4654afc4d5401221","tid":2507160,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ec54fc3ece0e29bfb30083b6ece422701fb1e3f8","tid":2507160,"uid":66324,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T23:32:15.000Z","msg":"點解會去印度留學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T23:39:25.000Z","msg":"一年70萬中國留學生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-f00a5dcf49227ad8d72071020cd90732_1440w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic3.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-f00a5dcf49227ad8d72071020cd90732_1440w.jpg&h=0012c1aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36f83fcad5593ad627dbbd2c0be1534549e6fb83","tid":2507160,"uid":38121,"like":2,"d